{"tid":7491,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"想出jazz/fit既入嚟","createTime":"2016-11-28T00:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T12:38:07.000Z","uid":13495,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27efce240fc4f9e924e9933e6b377c91100c9b2e","tid":7491,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:19:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=a5nv5%2FlCvFTWsFtK5xrHXsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=a23fe43a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】沙田吐露港公路發生三車串燒兩傷意外。一輛私家車，晚上近7時沿吐露港公路往九龍方向駛至科學園附近，司機因應交通情況減速停下，豈料，尾隨黃色本田Jazz收掣不及，撞向私家車尾。兩車司機準備落車理論之際，另一輛客貨車馳至，「嘭」一聲，猛力撼向Jazz，導致該車半截車身縮起，繼而衝前再一次撞及前面私家車。 <br />\n<br />\nJazz上姓李(25歲)男司機與同齡姓劉女乘客，背及腰部痛楚，同被困車內，其他司機見狀報警。消防員到場將兩名傷者救出送院，其餘兩名俱姓陳(34及54歲)男司機無恙，警方封鎖現場調查。意外引致現場交通非常擠塞，直至肇事車輛移走後，交通始恢復正常。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/28/081639_61be32bd9c2c969b5a546d535dd97d8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F28%2F081639_61be32bd9c2c969b5a546d535dd97d8c.jpg&h=b03b0a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Q4eEh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Q4eEh.jpg&h=ee45e969&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161127/mobile/bkn-20161127220314085-1127_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161127%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20161127220314085-1127_00822_001.html&d=a5nv5%2FlCvFTWsFtK5xrHXsW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=01b2d7f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161127/mobile/bkn-20161127220314085-1127_00822_001.html</a></span><br />\n<br />\n不如一人夾幾蚊俾車主去買返個車尾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBetween架車應該仲行到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83387d3f95dbd8e4b82deb3a7c4bfb3ca2c73967","tid":7491,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:22:46.000Z","msg":"另一輛<span style=\"color: red;\">客貨車</span>馳至 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e47878105278f3e24cdd109a0b95d597f10c208","tid":7491,"uid":2601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:22:58.000Z","msg":"個人冇事先做到世界冠軍架嘛"},{"pid":"c25604296339442d57f8893ff308a365b7f41495","tid":7491,"uid":6324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:23:31.000Z","msg":"後座有人的話"},{"pid":"37112348182095cd66635772831d7bb28169c8fe","tid":7491,"uid":19282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T00:33:34.000Z","msg":"又摺得幾工整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f1d3df65d5b085e67b7565712beb796f97fe3e","tid":7491,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T01:24:35.000Z","msg":"萬事得：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/28/092431_9daf2ce56a323a107317c2efd0ee4d8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F28%2F092431_9daf2ce56a323a107317c2efd0ee4d8d.jpg&h=15a70525&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbad7e2ca08bf53d47bf39296b35bba145dd806d","tid":7491,"uid":23536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T01:26:08.000Z","msg":"嘩屌 變左兩個轆"},{"pid":"60cae03d3cd8ae4d7a1a4f7a216549313cb6a753","tid":7491,"uid":13495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T01:26:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嘩屌 變左兩個轆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理論上仲行到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c4b22274cde19a1a023ace7734